# Monthly premium calculator API
Description:
-----------------
Implementation of Premium calculator API
This application/api is used to get all the available Occupation list and Calculate the monthly premium as per the business logic.
Functionality:
-----------------
1. CalculatePremium
  Desc : to calculate the premium as per the business requirement return the premium value.
  url : /api/PremiumCalculation/CalculatePremium  
  sample input: {"DeathCoverAmount":12285.5,"RatingID":2,"Age":35}
  sample output: 6449.887500
2. GetOccupationList
  url: /api/PremiumCalculation/GetOccupationList
  Desc : to retrieve all the OccupationList as per the master data and return the list.  
  sample output: JSON data list
